# Project Overview: Appraisily

Appraisily is a professional art and antique appraisal platform built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Technologies
- React 18
- TypeScript
- Vite build system
- Tailwind CSS
- Radix UI primitives with shadcn/ui
- React Router v6
- Supabase for backend functionality
- Stripe for payment processing
- Firebase for authentication
- Netlify for deployment

## Main Entry Points
- [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx) - Application entry point
- [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) - Application routes and layout
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global styles

## Core Functionality
The application provides art and antique appraisal services, with both free AI-powered artwork analysis and comprehensive professional appraisals.
